<plot>The third and final part of the Flip the Coin documentary series about the effects of globalization, this film documents poor financial rewards and toxic work conditions in tea plantations in Kenya, Sri Lanka, India and Bangladesh despite their associations with major Western tea brands and the Max Havelaar fair trade organization.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?197781</url></doc>
